This directory holds the snowflake-arctic-embed-xs.onnx model file.

The real model must be downloaded separately and placed here as:
  core-logic/src/main/assets/snowflake-arctic-embed-xs.onnx

Source: https://huggingface.co/Snowflake/snowflake-arctic-embed-xs
Export format: ONNX (opset 14+), input shape [1, seq_len]
Expected output: float32 tensor [1, 384]

EmbeddingProvider.initialize() will fail silently if the model is absent,
returning zero-vectors as a fallback until the model is present.
